cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with defending against adversarial attacks on deep neural networks, which is a common problem in the fields of machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the use of loss functions and retraining of networks, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
